						               													<description>Publisher Blurb:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This tactical sourcebook explores the various theaters of the early days of the Alternate Second World War and the operations that took place in them. Fields of War contains numerous tactical scenario seeds for the Gear Krieg universe that can be played together or separately, along with sample strike forces and heroes, special rules and miniature modeling advice for both the tabletop and the Gear Krieg miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fields of War includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Rules for Natural, Urban and Combat Engineering tabletop features; &amp;#10;- Scenario seeds for the above environments; &amp;#10;- Modeling instructions for both the tabletop and miniatures; &amp;#10;- New Heroes and equipment for Germany, the British Commonwealth, the United States, Soviet Russia and Imperial Japan; &amp;#10;- and several new vehicles and variants.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A copy of the Gear Krieg Rulebook, a few six-sided dice, miniatures/counters, pen and paper are required to use this supplement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
